snippet.title: Cobalt Alpha 116 ingame and editor footage.
snippet.description:
Footage of Cobalt Alpha 116.
Cobalt is a 2D platformer developed by Oxeye Game Studio in collaboration with Mojang. 
The game currently features several game modes ranging from single player challenges to local multiplayer as well as editors for creating your own maps.

Alpha access is available upon pre-order.
Visit www.playcobalt.com for more information!

Get the Cobalt EP by Anosou at http://anosou.bandcamp.com/album/cobalt-ep
